  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "HK MK23 .45 ACP手枪",
      "en": "HK MK23 .45 ACP pistol"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "MK23",
      "en": "MK23"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "HK MK23是一款发射.45 ACP弹药的大型半自动手枪，专为进攻型手枪用途设计。其USSOCOM版本配备激光瞄准模块（LAM）与消音器。该枪在美国特种作战司令部（USSOCOM）的选型中击败了最接近的竞争对手——柯尔特OHWS系统，最终被美国特种作战司令部采用并配发特种作战单位。这款手枪的研发始于1991年，当时特种作战部队代表提出需要一种\"特种作战专用进攻型手枪武器系统\"，首批手枪于1996年5月交付特种作战单位。",
      "en": "The HK MK23 is a semi-automatic large-frame pistol chambered in .45 ACP, designed specifically to be an offensive pistol. The USSOCOM version of the MK23 came paired with a laser aiming module (LAM) and suppressor. The USSOCOM MK23 was adopted by the United States Special Operations Command (USSOCOM) for special operations units, beating out the nearest competitor, Colt's OHWS. Development of the pistol began in 1991 as special operations representatives identified the need for an Offensive Handgun Weapons System—Special Operations Peculiar, and delivery of the pistols began in May 1996 to the special operation units."
    },
